data.description: Assumable Low-Rate Loan Option!! Lovely ranch style home situated on 8.749 partially wooded acres in West Union. There is a stream and cleared field at backed of property. Large circular driveway leads to the one car attached garage and the 24x24 detached garage. Additional 12x20 shed with built-in work bench. Low Maintenace vinyl wrap-around deck meticulously landscaped. Vaulted ceilings and two walls of windows give a bright spacious look to this open floor plan. Updated eat-in kitchen with island and stainless-steel appliances. Hardwood and tile floors throughout. Gas fireplace (two full propane tanks). Large primary bedroom with two closets and private full bath with oversized shower. There is a 2nd nice sized bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry room. Water purifier/filtration system installed in 2022. Pictures don't do it justice so come see!
